}
</style><section class="hearth-hero"><div class="hearth-hero__copy"><div class="hearth-hero__eyebrow"><span class="hearth-hero__pip"></span><span>Interior design studio</span></div><h1 class="hearth-hero__headline">Rooms that feel like <em>you</em>, only calmer.</h1><p class="hearth-hero__lede">We design warm, liveable interiors for people who host — one long project, then a home you never want to leave.</p><div class="hearth-hero__actions"><a class="hearth-btn hearth-btn--primary hearth-btn--lg" href="#cta" data-lessgo-cta="" data-lessgo-cta-role="primary">Book a call</a><a class="hearth-btn hearth-btn--ghost hearth-btn--lg" href="#cta" data-lessgo-cta="" data-lessgo-cta-role="secondary">See our work</a><span class="hearth-hero__caption">Booking Q3 2026</span></div><p class="hearth-hero__cta-subtext">Free consult · no obligation</p></div><div class="hearth-hero__art" aria-hidden="true"><div class="hearth-hero__photo hearth-hero__photo--main" style="background-image:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--clay), var(--accent))"></div></div></section></div><div id="services" data-surface="cream-2" style="scroll-margin-top:80px"><style>
.hearth-services {
