}
.hearth-service-card__cta {
  font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--accent-deep); margin-top: auto;
}
</style><section class="hearth-services"><div class="hearth-services__head"><div class="hearth-eyebrow">Our approach</div><h2 class="hearth-section-title">What we do</h2><p class="hearth-section-lede">Three ways we take a room from bare to belonging.</p></div><div class="hearth-services__grid"><article class="hearth-service-card"><div class="hearth-service-card__icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-sparkles" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z"></path><path d="M20 3v4"></path><path d="M22 5h-4"></path><path d="M4 17v2"></path><path d="M5 18H3"></path></svg></div><div class="hearth-service-card__num">01.</div><h3 class="hearth-service-card__title">Full-home design</h3><p class="hearth-service-card__desc">Concept to install, room by room, on one coherent thread.</p><span class="hearth-service-card__cta">Learn more →</span></article><article class="hearth-service-card"><div class="hearth-service-card__icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-palette" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22a1 1 0 0 1 0-20 10 9 0 0 1 10 9 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-2.25a1.75 1.75 0 0 0-1.4 2.8l.3.4a1.75 1.75 0 0 1-1.4 2.8z"></path><circle cx="13.5" cy="6.5" r=".5" fill="currentColor"></circle><circle cx="17.5" cy="10.5" r=".5" fill="currentColor"></circle><circle cx="6.5" cy="12.5" r=".5" fill="currentColor"></circle><circle cx="8.5" cy="7.5" r=".5" fill="currentColor"></circle></svg></div><div class="hearth-service-card__num">02.</div><h3 class="hearth-service-card__title">Colour & material</h3><p class="hearth-service-card__desc">A palette that holds together in every light, all year.</p><span class="hearth-service-card__cta">Learn more →</span></article><article class="hearth-service-card"><div class="hearth-service-card__icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-ruler" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.3 15.3a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 0 3.4l-2.6 2.6a2.4 2.4 0 0 1-3.4 0L2.7 8.7a2.41 2.41 0 0 1 0-3.4l2.6-2.6a2.41 2.41 0 0 1 3.4 0Z"></path><path d="m14.5 12.5 2-2"></path><path d="m11.5 9.5 2-2"></path><path d="m8.5 6.5 2-2"></path><path d="m17.5 15.5 2-2"></path></svg></div><div class="hearth-service-card__num">03.</div><h3 class="hearth-service-card__title">Space planning</h3><p class="hearth-service-card__desc">Flow, storage, and the small dimensions that make a room work.</p><span class="hearth-service-card__cta">Learn more →</span></article></div></section></div><div id="testimonials" data-surface="cream-2" style="scroll-margin-top:80px"><style>
